    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087860/extras/f5b4379e9909aaae8af44a5cf3795e71.avif?t=1771278940\" width=500 height=143 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一头中世纪的猪，被从家里绑架并带到某个地方。你几乎不记得你的过去，周围的世界对你来说既陌生又陌生。奇迹般地逃脱了绑架者的掌控，你必须踏上一段危险的旅程，穿越未知的土地！发现它们的秘密，找回你的记忆！一头猪能完成这样的壮举吗？哼哼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087860/extras/c79daf1b17aa4b04d59663aa413069fe.poster.avif?t=1771278940\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087860/extras/c79daf1b17aa4b04d59663aa413069fe.webm?t=1771278940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087860/extras/612c2d5c701bc65d7bedc1daa4353d07.avif?t=1771278940\" width=500 height=142 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在这个冒险中，你将</strong>：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集资源</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作物品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造房屋</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >耐心地听对话</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，还有为了你的猪命而战斗！<br><br>你面前是一个完全开放的世界。按照你的小猪心所指的任何方向前进吧！根据你的意愿完成或忽略任务，但请记住，你的决定可能会导致最意想不到的后果！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087860/extras/a2dee5fa4015f6a954afecddd1e81b89.poster.avif?t=1771278940\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087860/extras/a2dee5fa4015f6a954afecddd1e81b89.webm?t=1771278940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
